beer.beer_name: Fresh Harvest IPA - DDH West Coast IPA
beer.beer_description:
Once a year hops are harvested and sent to the 
brewers around the world. We have squeezed
the essential oils out of the freshest hops to
create the purest west coast IPA.
 “Beer for food & friends.”
